---
layout: base.njk
title: Devblog
permalink: /devblog.html
description: "Near-daily build logs on a self-hosted homelab, the automation that runs it, and Loupe, my photo app."
next:
  href: /davidisdeploying.html
  label: Projects
---
<main>
  <div class="phero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Working notes</div>
    <h1>Dev<em>blog</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">One post for each thing that clicked while I built it: a self-hosted homelab, the automation and search systems that run it, my photo app Loupe, and the smaller tools in between. It runs from cloud fundamentals up to the systems I keep alive at home.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bloglist" style="padding-bottom:0">
    <div class="shead"><span class="lbl">Start here</span><span class="rule"></span></div>
    {% include "starthere.njk" %}
  </div>
  {%- if collections.topics | length %}
  <details class="topiccloud">
    <summary class="shead"><span class="lbl">Topics</span><span class="tcount">{{ collections.topics | length }}</span><span class="chev">&#9662;</span><span class="rule"></span><a class="maplink" href="/stack.html">Stack map &rarr;</a></summary>
    <div class="topics">{% for t in collections.topics %}<a href="/devblog/topic/{{ t.slug }}.html">{{ t.topic }}<span class="ct">{{ t.count }}</span></a>{% endfor %}</div>
  </details>
  {%- endif %}
  <div class="bloglist"><div class="posts">
  {%- for post in collections.post | reverse %}
    <a class="pcard" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <div class="pmeta">{{ post.data.date | readable }}</div>
      <div class="ptitle">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
      <div class="psum">{{ post.data.summary }}</div>
      {%- if post.data.topics %}<div class="topics">{% for t in post.data.topics %}<span>{{ t }}</span>{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}
    </a>
  {%- endfor %}
  </div></div>
</main>
